content.p: Use the below links to purchase a membership or promotional pass, renew your membership and pre-book your activities. If you already have an active online account with us, please login below. Login to your account here with your University credentials. Login to your account here with your email and password. If you are new to University of Nottingham Sport (and haven't had an online account with us previously), please register for an online account with us below. If you are a University of Nottingham student or staff, please use your University email address if you have it. You'll be asked to select your preferred sports centre, please choose the one you expect to use most. +44 (0)115 748 7000 sport@nottingham.ac.uk Find our opening times here.
